   <title>Specifying Filter Values in Columns</title>
   <conbody>
     <p>You can type in explicit values to "filter by" at the top of each column of a grid as shown
      in Figure 2-4 below. The <uicontrol>hyperlink</uicontrol> column is filtered using the value
        <codeph>=http://www.slashdot.org</codeph>.</p>
